('da58669a-2309-539b-921e-a996d77413d6', '798d7cd2-13ea-442f-b1d6-3ce74db3b05d', 'SENIOR_HIGH', 'He struggled to fix the broken ___ on his jacket before rushing to the bus stop.', '他在趕往公車站之前，努力修理好夾克上壞掉的拉鍊。', 'zipper', 'button', 'buckle', 'clasp', 'zip (拉上拉鍊) + -er (表示物或工具) → zipper (拉鍊)', '想像拉鍊拉上時發出的 ''zip'' 聲音，加上 -er 就變成了拉鍊。', '2026-07-06 10:21:55', '2026-07-06 10:21:55');
